@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dhlclt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((0.68 - v2) / tmp)
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.93)) / (tmp + (v0 + 0.44 - v2 + 0.01)))
    v2 = wp.sin((0.67 / 0.53))
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
